N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8ยง 2.1 - Amendments

State Regulations

No proposal to amend this Chapter shall be considered unless
the proposed amendment and notice of intention to bring up the same shall have
been mailed to each Regent at least 10 days previous to the meeting at which
such amendment is to be considered. Notes
